        澶嶇敤瀵硅薄鏌ヨ宸叉湁鐨勫悓姝ラ€昏緫锛圡ysqlCache.replace_cleaned_all锛夛紝
        鍐欏叆瀵硅薄-{name} 琛紝涓?JOIN 璇昏〃涓€鑷淬€?""
        from PyQt6.QtWidgets import QMessageBox
        from PyQt6.QtCore import QObject, pyqtSignal

        mgr = getattr(self, '_report_manager', None)
        if not mgr:
            return
        rpt = mgr.get_report(report_id)
        if not rpt:
            return

        # 鍚屾鏃х紪杈戝櫒鐨勫瓧娈甸『搴忓埌 ReportDefinition锛堢‘淇?MySQL 琛ㄥ垪椤哄簭涓庣紪杈戠晫闈竴鑷达級
